就是其中之一。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-carter-the-rattlesnakes-announce-new-album-dark-rainbow-and-world-tour-3505266">Frank Carter &amp; The Rattlesnakes 宣布新专辑《Dark Rainbow》和世界巡演的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
